<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们感觉已经等了好几个小时。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们手里紧紧拿着旗子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一定要在火车拐过弯道并撞到石头和树之前让它停下来！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能彼得的手表坏了，火车已经开过去了。”菲利斯焦急地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但终于，火车的汽笛声响起，一缕白烟冒了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快挥动旗子！”彼得大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比，别站在铁轨上！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车轰隆隆地开了过来，非常非常快！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好！他们看不见我们！”鲍比大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>插在铁轨两旁的旗子摇晃着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一面旗子倒下，掉进了铁轨里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比跑过去，捡起旗子，挥动起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车飞快地开过来，越来越近了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比，不要站在铁轨上！”彼得警告她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这样不行！”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比，往后退！”菲利斯大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是鲍比大喊：“不行！现在还不行！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她仍然站在铁轨上，不停地挥动着两面旗子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车头看上去又黑又大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108081</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“停，停，停！”鲍比大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但没人能听见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得和菲利斯听不到鲍比的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是鲍比觉得火车应该是听到了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为它很快就慢了下来，停在离鲍比二十米远的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比看到巨大的黑火车头停下来了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她还是不停地挥着旗子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车司机和添煤工跳下火车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得和菲利斯向他们跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比动不了，因为她的腿抖得厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当大家回来找鲍比时，她躺在地上，手里还拿着旗子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她晕倒了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车司机把她抱起来，放在头等车厢的椅子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得人死了就是这个样子。”菲利斯小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要胡说！”彼得严厉地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车又开回了车站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，鲍比叹了口气，睁开眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她转身哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得和菲利斯不再担心了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为他们虽然没有见过她晕倒，但是见过她哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车到达火车站时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一群人来欢迎鲍比、彼得和菲利斯三位小英雄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家夸奖孩子们有勇气，有魄力！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们真是又聪明又勇敢！”火车司机说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯很享受此刻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从来没有当过英雄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得的耳朵红了，但是他也很开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有鲍比想要赶快离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火车公司可能会联系你们。”站长说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比不想再听到相关的事了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拉了拉彼得的夹克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“走吧，我想回家！”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她还在想铁轨上的石堆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果火车撞到了石堆会发生什么事呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们离开的时候，火车站站长、保安和火车司机们都为他们欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>